---

<div class="container" id="contacto">
  <h2>Contacto</h2>
  <div class="contacto-content">
    <div class="contacto-form">
      <form>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="nombre">Nombre</label>
          <input type="text" id="nombre" name="nombre" required />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="mensaje">Mensaje</label>
          <textarea id="mensaje" name="mensaje" rows="5" required></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-enviar">Enviar Mensaje</button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="contacto-info">
      <h3>Conecta conmigo</h3>
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" class="social-link">
          <span class="social-icon">💻</span>
          <span class="social-text">GitHub</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" class="social-link">
          <span class="social-icon">💼</span>
          <span class="social-text">LinkedIn</span>
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:tu@email.com" class="social-link">
          <span class="social-icon">📧</span>
          <span class="social-text">Email</span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com" target="_blank" class="social-link">
          <span class="social-icon">𝕏</span>
          <span class="social-text">Twitter</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="contacto-description">
        <p>¿Tienes una idea o proyecto en mente? Me encantaría colaborar contigo. No dudes en ponerte en contacto!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .container {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .container h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: transparent; 
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .contacto-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .contacto-form form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .form-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .form-group label {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .form-group input,
  .form-group textarea {
    background: var(--primary-light);
    border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-family: inherit;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .form-group input:focus,
  .form-group textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
  }

  .btn-enviar {
    background: white;
    border: none;
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: black;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .btn-enviar:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px white;
  }

  .contacto-info h3 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: var(--accent-bright);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .social-links {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .social-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    background: transparent;
    backdrop-filter: blur(1px);
    border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .social-link:hover {
  
 
    backdrop-filter: blur(3px);
  }

  .social-icon {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }

  .social-text {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent-bright);
  }

  .contacto-description {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.05);
    border: 2px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .contacto-description p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .contacto-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .container {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .container h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .social-links {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
